snippet.title: The Forest – PSX 2017: Multiplayer Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
The Forest, coming to playstation in 2018! Build a small
camp or a large ocean side fortress. Craft weapons from sticks and stones. Fight to stay alive against a vicious enemy force. Experience in singleplayer or with friends in cooperative
multiplayer!

http://survivetheforest.com/

Rated Mature: Intense Violence, Partial Nudity 

Endnight Games Ltd
